title: Mac Pro 2009 No image
message:
Hi guys,

I have this beautiful machine in for repair - Mac Pro from 2009 Quad Core version. 

No image, no chime, no caps led but I do get all diagnostics led ON:
CPU A 
CPU B
5V
3V
EFI 
GPU

Tested video card on another machine and it works.
Any idea why I am not getting an image?

Thanks,
Max

title: Mac Pro 2009 No image
message: The usual back plane failure. No schematics or anything for these. Hopeless...
